    <string name="guide_title">Match Block Fun - Guide</string>
    <string name="guide_sec1_title">1. Basic Rules</string>
    <string name="guide_sec1_desc">Tap tiles to put them in slots. Match 3 identical tiles to clear them. If all 7 slots are filled, you lose.</string>
    <string name="guide_sec2_title">2. Game Items</string>
    <string name="guide_sec2_desc">Move Out: Move first 3 tiles out of slots.\nShuffle: Shuffle all remaining tiles on board.\nUndo: Undo last tap.</string>
    <string name="guide_sec3_title">3. Getting Coins</string>
    <string name="guide_sec3_desc">Get coins from daily sign-in and first-time level clears. Winning PvP matches also awards coins!</string>
    <string name="guide_sec4_title">4. Store Exchange</string>
    <string name="guide_sec4_desc">Exchange coins for game items or custom tile skins in the Shop.</string>
    <string name="guide_sec5_title">5. PvP Rules</string>
    <string name="guide_sec5_desc">Clear tiles in PvP to get energy. Use energy to attack:\nFog (cost 3): Hide opponent\'s board.\nShrink (cost 6): Lock one slot for opponent.\nSeal (cost 10): Hide all visible cards for opponent.</string>

